		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#a28631" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#a28631">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="62" y="368" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="430" height="81" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" color="#ffffff">辖域守护者</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="437" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">愚妄之眼：每次会分别记录<span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>的攻击次数，当某一元素计数达</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3次</span><span>时，即为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">记录完成</span><span>，完成后</span><span color="#ffdfbf">对应抗性+70%</span><span>(特化</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+130%</span><span>)，并获得对应元素提升和自附着。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守护者进行抓、抓、翼斩3段普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#ffe599">25%,25%,50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="374" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守护者举剑，迅速转圈袭击，造成<span color="#ffe599">33%,33%,34%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离守护者较远时，守护者直接朝前方猛戳，造成<span color="#ffe599">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="413" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离守护者较远时，守护者劈出2道岩刃，均造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于元素形态25-30s后，守望者将汇集自身元素，凝于一滴后掷于地面，造成<span color="#ffffbf">对应元素的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">150%</span><span>伤害，同时退出元素形态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
