		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="425" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守护者立即进入<span textDecoration="underline">愚妄之眼</span><span>状态，持续5s；未成功记录将造成</span><span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害，成功记录则转为对应元素形态，该元素抗性</span><span color="#ffdfbf">提升70%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ffdfbf">特化130%</span><span>)，并获得</span><span color="#ffdfbf">自附着</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
